# Progress Log

## Current State

**Version**: 1.5.1 | **Repo**: `Dark-Riders/Ultimate-Image-Tools` | **Deployed**: GitHub Pages (`docs/`)

**Architecture**: 3-tab app (Applier / Creator / BG Remover) served by Bun HTTP server on port 19683.
- **Applier** (`app.js`): Bulk watermark overlay with drag & drop, folder uploads, ZIP download.
- **Creator** (`public/creator/`, 10 files): Watermark template builder using `window.Creator` namespace. 40 borders, badges, QR, diagonal text.
- **BG Remover** (`public/remover/`, 10 files): AI background removal + manual tools. Uses bare `var` globals with lazy DOM init. Features: pre-mask (keep/remove brush, magic wand, edge-aware quick select with Sobel), post-mask editor, compose mode.
- **Server** (`src/server.ts`): Bun + Sharp, serves static files and processes watermark API requests.
- **Docs** (`docs/`): Mirror of `public/` with `./` relative paths for GitHub Pages.

**Key shortcuts** (mask/premask mode): `[ ]` brush size, `{ }` tolerance, `Ctrl+Z` undo.

**Critical gotchas**: See `agent-notes.md` § Gotchas — especially global scope collisions (`const` vs `var`, `window.images`) and CSS hidden attribute override.

> Older entries archived in `progress-archive.log`.

